## ⚙️ Installation & Setup

### 1. Clone the repository
```bash
git clone https://github.com/yourusername/it-club-system.git
cd it-club-system
```

### 2. Frontend Setup (Root Directory)
```bash
npm install
```

### 3. Backend Setup
```bash
cd server
npm install
```

### 4. Database Setup
- Create a `.env` file in the `server` directory.
- Add your database connection string and JWT secrets (refer to `.env.example`).
- Run Prisma migrations:
```bash
npx prisma migrate dev
```

